msgstr ":doc:`discuss/chatter`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:3
msgid "Chatter"
msgstr "Chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:8
msgid ""
"The *Chatter* feature is integrated throughout Odoo to streamline "
"communication, maintain traceability, and provide accountability among team "
"members. Chatter windows, known as *composers*, are located on almost every "
"record within the database, and allow users to communicate with both "
"internal users and external contacts."
msgstr ""
"*Chatter*-funktionen er integreret i hele Odoo for at strømline "
"kommunikation, opretholde sporbarhed og sikre ansvarlighed blandt "
"teammedlemmer. Chatter-vinduer, kendt som *editorer*, findes på næsten alle "
"poster i databasen og giver brugere mulighed for at kommunikere med både "
"interne brugere og eksterne kontakter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:13
msgid ""
"Chatter composers also enable users to log notes, upload files, and schedule "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Chatter-editorer gør det også muligt for brugere at logge noter, uploade "
"filer og planlægge aktiviteter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:16
msgid "Chatter thread"
msgstr "Chatter-tråd"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:18
msgid ""
"A *chatter thread* can be found on most pages in the database, and serves as "
"a record of the updates and edits made to a record. A note is logged in the "
"chatter thread when a change is made. The note includes details of the "
"change, and a time stamp."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:23
msgid ""
"A user, Mitchell Admin, needs to update the email address of a contact. "
"After they save the changes to the contact record, a note is logged in the "
"chatter of the contact record with the following information:"
msgstr ""
"En bruger, Mitchell Admin, skal opdatere e-mailadressen på en kontakt. Efter "
"de har gemt ændringerne på kontaktposten, logges en note i chatter på "
"kontaktposten med følgende oplysninger:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:27
msgid "The date when the change occurred."
msgstr "Datoen hvor ændringen fandt sted."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:28
msgid "The email address as it was previously listed."
msgstr "E-mailadressen som den tidligere var anført."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:29
msgid "The updated email address."
msgstr "Den opdaterede e-mailadresse."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid "A close up of a chatter thread with an update to a contact record."
msgstr "Nærbillede af en chatter-tråd med en opdatering til en kontaktpost."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:35
msgid ""
"If a record was created, or edited, via an imported file, or was otherwise "
"updated through an intervention by the system, the chatter thread creates a "
"log note, and credits the change to OdooBot."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en post blev oprettet eller redigeret via en importeret fil, eller på "
"anden måde blev opdateret gennem en systemindgriben, opretter chatter-tråden "
"en lognote og krediterer ændringen til OdooBot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "A close up of a chatter thread of an OdooBot created contact record."
msgstr "Nærbillede af en chatter-tråd for en kontaktpost oprettet af OdooBot."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:46
msgid "Add followers"
msgstr "Tilføj følgere"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:48
msgid ""
"A *follower* is a user or contact that is added to a record and is notified "
"when the record is updated, based on specific :ref:`follower subscription "
"settings <discuss/edit-subscription>`. Followers can add themselves, or can "
"be added by another user."
msgstr ""
"En *følger* er en bruger eller kontakt, der tilføjes til en post og "
"underrettes, når posten opdateres, baseret på specifikke :ref:`indstillinger "
"for følgerabonnement <discuss/edit-subscription>`. Følgere kan tilføje sig "
"selv eller kan tilføjes af en anden bruger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:53
msgid ""
"If a user creates, or is assigned to a record, they are automatically added "
"as a follower."
msgstr ""
"Pokud uživatel vytvoří záznam nebo je mu přiřazen, je automaticky přidán "
"jako sledující."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:55
msgid ""
"To follow a record, navigate to any record with a chatter thread. For "
"example, to open a *Helpdesk* ticket, navigate to :menuselection:`Helpdesk "
"app --> Tickets --> All Tickets`, and select a ticket from the list to open "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li sledovat záznam, přejděte na libovolný záznam s vláknem chatteru. "
"Například pro otevření tiketu aplikace *Kundeservice* přejděte na "
":menuselection:`Kundeservice --> Tikety --> Všechny tikety` a vyberte tiket "
"ze seznamu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:59
msgid ""
"At the top-right, above the chatter composer, click :guilabel:`Follow`. "
"Doing this changes the button to read :guilabel:`Following`. Click it again "
"to :guilabel:`Unfollow`."
msgstr ""
"V pravém horním rohu nad editorem chatteru klikněte na :guilabel:`Sledovat`. "
"Tlačítko se změní na :guilabel:`Sleduji`. Kliknutím znovu volbu "
":guilabel:`Přestat sledovat`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:63
msgid "Manage followers"
msgstr "Správa sledujících"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:65
msgid ""
"To add another user, or contact, as a follower, click the |user|. This opens "
"a drop-down list of the current followers. Click :guilabel:`Add Followers` "
"to open an :guilabel:`Invite Follower` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li přidat dalšího uživatele nebo kontakt jako sledujícího, klikněte "
"na |user|. Otevře se rozbalovací seznam aktuálních sledujících. Klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Přidat sledující` a otevře se vyskakovací okno :guilabel:`Pozvat "
"sledujícího`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:69
msgid ""
"Select one or more contacts from the :guilabel:`Recipients` drop-down list. "
"To notify the contacts, tick the :guilabel:`Send Notification` checkbox. "
"Edit the message template as desired, then click :guilabel:`Add Followers`."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte jeden nebo více kontaktů z rozbalovacího seznamu "
":guilabel:`Příjemci`. Chcete-li kontakty upozornit, zaškrtněte políčko "
":guilabel:`Odeslat meddelelse`. Upravte šablonu zprávy podle potřeby a "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Přidat sledující`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:73
msgid ""
"To remove followers, click the |user| to open the current followers list. "
"Find the name of the follower to be removed, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"remove` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li odebrat sledující, klikněte na |user| a otevřete seznam aktuálních "
"sledujících. Najděte jméno sledujícího, kterého chcete odebrat, a klikněte "
"na ikonu :icon:`fa-remove` :guilabel:`(odebrat)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:79
msgid "Edit follower subscription"
msgstr "Úprava odběru sledujícího"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:81
msgid ""
"The updates a follower receives can vary based on their subscription "
"settings. To see the type of updates a follower is subscribed to, and to "
"edit the list, click the |user|. Find the appropriate follower in the list, "
"then click the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon. This opens "
"the :guilabel:`Edit Subscription` pop-up window for the follower."
msgstr ""
"Aktualizace, které sledující obdrží, se mohou lišit v závislosti na "
"nastavení odběru. Chcete-li zobrazit typ aktualizací, které sledující "
"odebírá, a upravit seznam, klikněte na |user|. Najděte příslušného "
"sledujícího v seznamu a klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`"
"(tužka)`. Otevře se vyskakovací okno :guilabel:`Upravit odběr` pro "
"sledujícího."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:86
msgid ""
"The list of available subscription settings varies depending on the record "
"type. For example, a follower of a *Helpdesk* ticket may be informed when "
"the ticket is rated. This option would not be available for the followers of "
"a *CRM* opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Seznam dostupných nastavení odběru se liší v závislosti na typu záznamu. "
"Například sledující tiketu aplikace *Kundeservice* může být informován, když "
"je tiket ohodnocen. Tato možnost nebude dostupná pro sledující příležitosti "
"v aplikaci *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:90
msgid ""
"Tick the checkbox for any updates the follower should receive, and clear the "
"checkbox for any updates they should **not** receive. "
"Click :guilabel:`Apply` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Zaškrtněte políčko u aktualizací, které by sledující měl přijímat, a zrušte "
"zaškrtnutí u aktualizací, které by **neměl** přijímat. Po dokončení klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Použít`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:97
msgid "The Edit Subscription window on a Helpdesk ticket."
msgstr "Okno Upravit odběr u tiketu Kundeservice."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:97
msgid ""
"The Edit Subscription options vary depending on the record type. These are "
"the options for a Helpdesk ticket."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti Upravit odběr se liší v závislosti na typu záznamu. Toto jsou "
"možnosti pro tiket Kundeservice."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:103
msgid "Log notes"
msgstr "Zaznamenání poznámek"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:105
msgid ""
"The chatter function includes the ability to log internal notes on "
"individual records. These notes are only accessible to internal users, and "
"are available on any records that feature a chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Funkce chatteru zahrnuje možnost zaznamenávat interní poznámky k jednotlivým "
"záznamům. Tyto poznámky jsou přístupné pouze interním uživatelům a jsou "
"dostupné u všech záznamů, které obsahují vlákno chatteru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:109
msgid ""
"To log an internal note, first navigate to a record. For example, to open a "
"*CRM* opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My "
"Pipeline`, and click on the Kanban card of an opportunity to open it. Then, "
"at the top-right, above the chatter composer, click :guilabel:`Log note`."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li zaznamenat interní poznámku, nejprve přejděte na záznam. Například "
"pro otevření příležitosti v aplikaci *CRM* přejděte na "
":menuselection:`CRM --> Salg --> Můj prodejní trychtýř` a klikněte na kartu "
"Kanban příležitosti. Poté v pravém horním rohu nad editorem chatteru "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Zaznamenat poznámku`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:114
msgid ""
"Enter the note in the chatter composer. To tag an internal user, type `@`, "
"and begin typing the name of the person to tag. Then, select a name from the "
"drop-down menu. Depending on their notification settings, the user is "
"notified by email, or through Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Zadejte poznámku do editoru chatteru. Chcete-li označit interního uživatele, "
"napište `@` a začněte psát jméno osoby, kterou chcete označit. Poté vyberte "
"jméno z rozbalovací nabídky. V závislosti na nastavení upozornění je "
"uživatel upozorněn e-mailem nebo prostřednictvím Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:119
msgid ""
"Outside contacts can also be tagged in an internal log note. The contact "
"then receives an email with the contents of the note they were tagged in, "
"including any attachments added directly to the note. If they respond to the "
"email, their response is logged in the chatter, and they are added to the "
"record as a follower."
msgstr ""
"Externí kontakty lze také označit v interní poznámce. Kontakt pak obdrží e-"
"mail s obsahem poznámky, ve které byl označen, včetně všech příloh přidaných "
"přímo k poznámce. Pokud odpoví na e-mail, jejich odpověď je zaznamenána v "
"chatteru a jsou přidáni k záznamu jako sledující."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:124
msgid ""
"Outside contacts are **not** able to log in to view the entire chatter "
"thread, and are only notified of specific updates, based on "
"their :ref:`follower subscription settings <discuss/edit-subscription>`, or "
"when they are tagged directly."
msgstr ""
"Externí kontakty **nemohou** se přihlásit a zobrazit celé vlákno chatteru a "
"jsou upozorňováni pouze na konkrétní aktualizace na základě jejich "
":ref:`nastavení odběru sledujícího <discuss/edit-subscription>` nebo když "
"jsou přímo označeni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:131
msgid "Send messages"
msgstr "Odesílání zpráv"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:133
msgid ""
"Chatter composers can send messages to outside contacts, without having to "
"leave the database, or open a different application. This makes it easy to "
"communicate with potential customers in the *Sales* and *CRM* applications, "
"or vendors in the *Purchase* app."
msgstr ""
"Chatter-kompositioner kan sende beskeder til eksterne kontakter uden at "
"skulle forlade databasen eller åbne en anden applikation. Dette gør det nemt "
"at kommunikere med potentielle kunder i *Salg*- og *CRM*-applikationerne "
"eller leverandører i *Indkøb*-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:137
msgid ""
"To send a message, first navigate to a record. For example, to send a "
"message from a *CRM* opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> "
"Sales --> My Pipeline`, and click on the Kanban card of an opportunity to "
"open it. Then, at the top-right, above the chatter composer, "
"click :guilabel:`Send message`."
msgstr ""
"For at sende en besked skal du først navigere til en post. For eksempel, for "
"at sende en besked fra en *CRM*-mulighed, naviger til :menuselection:`CRM-"
"app --> Salg --> Min pipeline`, og klik på Kanban-kortet for en mulighed for "
"at åbne den. Klik derefter øverst til højre, over chatter-kompositoren, på "
":guilabel:`Send besked`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:143
msgid ""
"Press :command:`Ctrl + Enter` to send a message, instead of using "
"the :guilabel:`Send` button."
msgstr ""
"Tryk på :command:`Ctrl + Enter` for at sende en besked i stedet for at bruge "
"knappen :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:145
msgid ""
"If any :ref:`followers <discuss/add-followers>` have been added to the "
"record, they are added as recipients of the message."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er tilføjet :ref:`følgere <discuss/add-followers>` til posten, "
"tilføjes de som modtagere af beskeden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:149
msgid ""
":ref:`Followers <discuss/add-followers>` of a record are added as recipients "
"of a message automatically. If a follower should **not** receive a message, "
"they must be removed as a follower before the message is sent, or a note is "
"logged."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Følgere <discuss/add-followers>` af en post tilføjes automatisk som "
"modtagere af en besked. Hvis en følger **ikke** skal modtage en besked, skal "
"vedkommende fjernes som følger, før beskeden sendes, eller en note logges."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid ""
"A chatter composer preparing to send a message to the followers of a CRM "
"opportunity and\n"
"the customer listed on the opportunity record."
msgstr ""
"En chatter-kompositor, der forbereder afsendelse af en besked til følgerne "
"af en CRM-mulighed og\n"
"kunden, der er anført på mulighedsposten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:159
msgid "Expand full composer"
msgstr "Udvid fuld kompositor"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:161
msgid ""
"The chatter composer can be expanded to a larger pop-up window, allowing for "
"additional customizations."
msgstr ""
"Chatter-kompositoren kan udvides til et større pop op-vindue, hvilket giver "
"mulighed for yderligere tilpasninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:164
msgid ""
"To open the full composer, click the :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(expand)` "
"icon in the bottom-right corner of the composer window."
msgstr ""
"For at åbne den fulde kompositor skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-expand` "
":guilabel:`(udvid)` i nederste højre hjørne af kompositorvinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:171
msgid "A chatter composer with emphasis on the expand icon."
msgstr "En chatter-kompositor med fokus på udvid-ikonet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:171
msgid "The expand icon in a chatter composer."
msgstr "Udvid-ikonet i en chatter-kompositor."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:173
msgid ""
"Doing this opens a :guilabel:`Compose Email` pop-up window. Confirm or edit "
"the intended :guilabel:`Recipients` of the message, or add additional "
"recipients. The :guilabel:`Subject` field auto-populates based on the title "
"of the record, though it can be edited, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner et :guilabel:`Skriv e-mail` pop op-vindue. Bekræft eller rediger "
"de tilsigtede :guilabel:`Modtagere` af beskeden, eller tilføj yderligere "
"modtagere. Feltet :guilabel:`Emne` udfyldes automatisk baseret på postens "
"titel, men det kan redigeres efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:177
msgid ""
"To use an :doc:`email template <../../general/companies/email_template/>` "
"for the message, select it from the drop-down menu in the :guilabel:`Load "
"template` field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:181
msgid ""
"The number and type of templates available vary, based on the record the "
"message is created from."
msgstr ""
"Antallet og typen af tilgængelige skabeloner varierer baseret på den post, "
"som beskeden oprettes fra."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:183
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(paperclip)` icon to add any files to "
"the message, then click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(papirclips)` for at tilføje "
"filer til beskeden, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "The expanded full chatter composer in the CRM application."
msgstr "Den udvidede fulde chatter-kompositor i CRM-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:191
msgid "Edit sent messages"
msgstr "Redigér sendte beskeder"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:193
msgid ""
"Messages can be edited after they are sent, to fix typos, correct mistakes, "
"or add missing information."
msgstr ""
"Beskeder kan redigeres, efter de er sendt, for at rette tastefejl, korrigere "
"fejl eller tilføje manglende information."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:197
msgid ""
"When messages are edited after they have been sent, an updated message is "
"**not** sent to the recipient."
msgstr ""
"Når beskeder redigeres, efter de er blevet sendt, sendes der **ikke** en "
"opdateret besked til modtageren."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:200
msgid ""
"To edit a sent message, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"h` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon menu to the right of the message. Then, "
"select :guilabel:`Edit`. Make any necessary adjustments to the message."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "The edit message option in a chatter thread."
msgstr "Muligheden for at redigere beskeder i en chatter-tråd."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:207
msgid ""
"To save the changes, press :command:`Ctrl + Enter`. To discard the changes, "
"press :command:`Escape`."
msgstr ""
"For at gemme ændringerne skal du trykke på :command:`Ctrl + Enter`. For at "
"kassere ændringerne skal du trykke på :command:`Escape`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:210
msgid ""
"Users with Admin-level access rights can edit any sent messages. Users "
"without Admin rights can **only** edit messages they created."
msgstr ""
"Brugere med administratoradgangsrettigheder kan redigere alle sendte "
"beskeder. Brugere uden administratorrettigheder kan **kun** redigere "
"beskeder, de selv har oprettet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:216
msgid "Search messages"
msgstr "Søg efter beskeder"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:218
msgid ""
"Chatter threads can become long after a while, because of all the "
"information they contain. To make it easier to find a specific entry, users "
"can search the text of messages and notes for specific keywords."
msgstr ""
"Chatter-tråde kan blive lange efter et stykke tid på grund af al den "
"information, de indeholder. For at gøre det lettere at finde en bestemt post "
"kan brugere søge i teksten i beskeder og noter efter specifikke nøgleord."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:222
msgid ""
"First, select a record with a chatter thread. For example, to search a *CRM* "
"opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My Pipeline`, "
"and click on the Kanban card of an opportunity to open it. Then, at the top-"
"right, above the chatter composer, click the :icon:`oi-"
"search` :guilabel:`(search)` icon to open the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Vælg først en post med en chatter-tråd. For eksempel, for at søge i en *CRM*-"
"mulighed skal du navigere til :menuselection:`CRM-app --> Salg --> Min "
"pipeline` og klikke på Kanban-kortet for en mulighed for at åbne den. Klik "
"derefter øverst til højre, over chatter-skriveren, på :icon:`oi-search` "
":guilabel:`søg`-ikonet for at åbne søgelinjen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:227
msgid ""
"Enter a keyword or phrase into the search bar, then hit :command:`Enter`, or "
"click the :icon:`oi-search` :guilabel:`(search)` icon to the right of the "
"search bar. Any messages or notes containing the keyword or phrase entered "
"are listed below the search bar, with the keyword highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Indtast et nøgleord eller en sætning i søgelinjen, og tryk derefter på "
":command:`Enter`, eller klik på :icon:`oi-search` :guilabel:`søg`-ikonet til "
"højre for søgelinjen. Alle beskeder eller noter, der indeholder det "
"indtastede nøgleord eller sætning, vises under søgelinjen med nøgleordet "
"fremhævet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:232
msgid ""
"To be taken directly to a particular message in the chatter thread, hover "
"over the upper-right corner of the result to reveal a :guilabel:`Jump` "
"button. Click this button to be directed to that message's location in the "
"thread."
msgstr ""
"For at blive taget direkte til en bestemt besked i chatter-tråden skal du "
"holde markøren over øverste højre hjørne af resultatet for at afsløre en "
":guilabel:`Hop til`-knap. Klik på denne knap for at blive dirigeret til den "
"pågældende beskeds placering i tråden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:240
msgid ""
"Search results in a chatter thread emphasising the search icon and the jump "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Søgeresultater i en chatter-tråd, der fremhæver søgeikonet og hop til-"
"knappen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:240
msgid ""
"Search results in a chatter thread. Hover over the upper-right corner of a "
"result to see the **Jump** option. Click it to be taken directly to that "
"message in the chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Søgeresultater i en chatter-tråd. Hold markøren over øverste højre hjørne af "
"et resultat for at se muligheden **Hop til**. Klik på den for at blive taget "
"direkte til den pågældende besked i chatter-tråden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:246
msgid "Schedule activities"
msgstr "Planlæg aktiviteter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:248
msgid ""
"*Activities* are follow-up tasks tied to a record in an Odoo database. "
"Activities can be scheduled on any database page that contains a chatter "
"thread, Kanban view, list view, or activities view of an application."
msgstr ""
"*Aktiviteter* er opfølgningsopgaver knyttet til en post i en Odoo-database. "
"Aktiviteter kan planlægges på enhver databaseside, der indeholder en chatter-"
"tråd, Kanban-visning, listevisning eller aktivitetsvisning af en applikation."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:252
msgid ""
"To schedule an activity through a chatter thread, click "
"the :guilabel:`Activities` button, located at the top of the chatter on any "
"record. On the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window that appears, "
"select an :guilabel:`Activity Type` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"For at planlægge en aktivitet via en chatter-tråd skal du klikke på "
":guilabel:`Aktiviteter`-knappen, der findes øverst i chatteren på enhver "
"post. I pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Planlæg aktivitet`, der vises, skal du "
"vælge en :guilabel:`Aktivitetstype` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:257
msgid ""
"Individual applications have a list of *Activity Types* dedicated to that "
"application. For example, to view and edit the activities available for the "
"*CRM* application, go to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> "
"Activity Types`."
msgstr ""
"Enkelte applikationer har en liste over *Aktivitetstyper*, der er dedikeret "
"til den pågældende applikation. For eksempel, for at se og redigere de "
"aktiviteter, der er tilgængelige for *CRM*-applikationen, skal du gå til "
":menuselection:`CRM-app --> Konfiguration --> Aktivitetstyper`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:261
msgid ""
"Enter a title for the activity in the :guilabel:`Summary` field, located in "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Indtast en titel for aktiviteten i feltet :guilabel:`Resumé`, der findes i "
"pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Planlæg aktivitet`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:264
msgid ""
"Select a name from the :guilabel:`Assigned to` drop-down menu to assign the "
"activity to a different user. Otherwise, the user creating the activity is "
"automatically assigned."
msgstr ""
"Vælg et navn fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Tildelt til` for at tildele "
"aktiviteten til en anden bruger. Ellers tildeles den bruger, der opretter "
"aktiviteten, automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:267
msgid ""
"Add any additional information in the optional :guilabel:`Log a note...` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj eventuelle yderligere oplysninger i det valgfrie felt :guilabel:`Log "
"en note...`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:270
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Due Date` field on the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up "
"window auto-populates based on the configuration settings for the "
"selected :guilabel:`Activity Type`. However, this date can be changed by "
"selecting a day on the calendar in the :guilabel:`Due Date` field."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Forfaldsdato` i pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Planlæg "
"aktivitet` udfyldes automatisk baseret på konfigurationsindstillingerne for "
"den valgte :guilabel:`Aktivitetstype`. Denne dato kan dog ændres ved at "
"vælge en dag i kalenderen i feltet :guilabel:`Forfaldsdato`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:274
msgid "Lastly, click one of the following buttons:"
msgstr "Klik til sidst på en af følgende knapper:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:276
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: adds the activity to the chatter "
"under :guilabel:`Planned activities`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planlæg`: tilføjer aktiviteten til chatteren under "
":guilabel:`Planlagte aktiviteter`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:277
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark as Done`: adds the details of the activity to the chatter "
"under :guilabel:`Today`. The activity is not scheduled, it is automatically "
"marked as completed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:279
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Done \\& Schedule Next`: adds the task under :guilabel:`Today` "
"marked as done, and opens a new activity window."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Udført og planlæg næste`: tilføjer opgaven under :guilabel:`I "
"dag` markeret som udført og åbner et nyt aktivitetsvindue."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:281
msgid ":guilabel:`Discard`: discards any changes made on the pop-up window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:283
msgid ""
"Scheduled activities are added to the chatter for the record "
"under :guilabel:`Planned activities`, and are color-coded based on their due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Planlagte aktiviteter tilføjes til chatteren for posten under "
":guilabel:`Planlagte aktiviteter` og er farvekodede baseret på deres "
"forfaldsdato."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:286
msgid "**Red** icons indicate an overdue activity."
msgstr "**Røde** ikoner angiver en forsinket aktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:287
msgid ""
"**Yellow** icons indicate an activity with a due date scheduled for the "
"current date."
msgstr ""
"**Gule** ikoner angiver en aktivitet med en forfaldsdato planlagt til dags "
"dato."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:288
msgid ""
"**Green** icons indicate an activity with a due date scheduled in the future."
msgstr ""
"**Grønne** ikoner angiver en aktivitet med en forfaldsdato planlagt i "
"fremtiden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid "A chatter thread with planned activities with varying due dates."
msgstr ""
"En chatter-tråd med planlagte aktiviteter med forskellige forfaldsdatoer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:295
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info)` icon next to a planned "
"activity to see additional details."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info)`-ikonet ved siden af en "
"planlagt aktivitet for at se yderligere detaljer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid "A detailed view of a planned activity."
msgstr "En detaljeret visning af en planlagt aktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:302
msgid ""
"After completing an activity, click :guilabel:`Mark Done` under the activity "
"entry in the chatter. This opens a :guilabel:`Mark Done` pop-up window, "
"where additional notes about the activity can be entered. After adding any "
"comments to the pop-up window, click: :guilabel:`Done \\& Schedule "
"Next`, :guilabel:`Done`, or :guilabel:`Discard`."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have gennemført en aktivitet skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Markér "
"som udført` under aktivitetsindgangen i chatteren. Dette åbner et pop op-"
"vindue :guilabel:`Markér som udført`, hvor yderligere noter om aktiviteten "
"kan indtastes. Efter at have tilføjet eventuelle kommentarer til pop op-"
"vinduet skal du klikke på: :guilabel:`Udført og planlæg næste`, "
":guilabel:`Udført` eller :guilabel:`Kassér`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:307
msgid ""
"After the activity is marked complete, an entry with the activity type, "
"title, and any other details that were included in the pop-up window are "
"listed in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Efter at aktiviteten er markeret som fuldført, vises en indgang med "
"aktivitetstypen, titlen og eventuelle andre detaljer, der var inkluderet i "
"pop op-vinduet, i chatteren."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:None
msgid ""
"A chatter thread with a completed activity, included additional details."
msgstr ""
"En chatter-tråd med en fuldført aktivitet, inkluderet yderligere detaljer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:317
msgid "Attach files"
msgstr "Vedhæft filer"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:319
msgid ""
"Files can be added as attachments in the chatter, either to send with "
"messages, or to include with a record."
msgstr ""
"Filer kan tilføjes som vedhæftninger i chatteren, enten til at sende med "
"beskeder eller til at inkludere i en post."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:323
msgid ""
"After a file has been added to a chatter thread, it can be downloaded by any "
"user with access to the thread. Click the |paperclip| to make the files "
"header visible, if necessary. Then, click the :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(download)` icon the file to download it."
msgstr ""
"Efter at en fil er blevet tilføjet til en chatter-tråd, kan den downloades "
"af enhver bruger med adgang til tråden. Klik på |paperclip| for at gøre "
"filhovedet synligt, hvis det er nødvendigt. Klik derefter på :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`(download)`-ikonet for at downloade filen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:327
msgid ""
"To attach a file, click the |paperclip| located at the top of the chatter "
"composer of any record that contains a chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"For at vedhæfte en fil skal du klikke på |paperclip|, der findes øverst i "
"chatter-composeren på enhver post, der indeholder en chatter-tråd."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:330
msgid ""
"This opens a file explorer pop-up window. Navigate to the desired file, "
"select it, then click :guilabel:`Open` to add it to the record. "
"Alternatively, files can be dragged and dropped directly onto a chatter "
"thread."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner et pop-op-vindue med en filbrowser. Naviger til den ønskede fil, "
"vælg den, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Åbn` for at tilføje den til posten. "
"Alternativt kan filer trækkes og slippes direkte på en chatter-tråd."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:334
msgid ""
"After files have been added, they are listed in the chatter thread, under "
"a :guilabel:`Files` heading."
msgstr ""
"Når filer er blevet tilføjet, vises de i chatter-tråden under overskriften "
":guilabel:`Filer`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:338
msgid ""
"After at least one file has been added to a chatter record, a new button "
"labeled :guilabel:`Attach files` appears below the :guilabel:`Files` "
"heading. To attach any additional files, this is the button that **must** be "
"used, instead of the |paperclip| at the top of the chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Når mindst én fil er blevet tilføjet til en chatter-post, vises en ny knap "
"med navnet :guilabel:`Vedhæft filer` under overskriften :guilabel:`Filer`. "
"For at vedhæfte yderligere filer **skal** denne knap bruges i stedet for "
"|paperclip| øverst i chatter-tråden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:343
msgid ""
"After the :guilabel:`Files` section heading appears in the thread, clicking "
"the |paperclip| no longer opens a file explorer pop-up window. Instead, "
"clicking the |paperclip| toggles the :guilabel:`Files` section from visible "
"to invisible in the chatter thread."
msgstr ""
"Når sektionsoverskriften :guilabel:`Filer` vises i tråden, åbner klik på "
"|paperclip| ikke længere et pop-op-vindue med en filbrowser. I stedet "
"skifter klik på |paperclip| sektionen :guilabel:`Filer` mellem synlig og "
"usynlig i chatter-tråden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:0
msgid ""
"A chatter thread with a file attached and the Attach files button added."
msgstr "En chatter-tråd med en vedhæftet fil og knappen Vedhæft filer tilføjet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:354
msgid "Integrations"
msgstr "Integrationer"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:356
msgid ""
"Beyond the standard features, additional integrations can be enabled to work "
"with the chatter feature, specifically *WhatsApp* and *Google Translate*."
msgstr ""
"Ud over standardfunktionerne kan yderligere integrationer aktiveres til at "
"fungere sammen med chatter-funktionen, specifikt *WhatsApp* og *Google "
"Translate*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:360
msgid ""
"Before the *WhatsApp* and *Google Translate* integrations can be used with "
"the chatter, they **must** be configured. Step-by-step instructions on how "
"to set-up each of these features can be found in the documentation below:"
msgstr ""
"Før *WhatsApp*- og *Google Translate*-integrationerne kan bruges med "
"chatteren, **skal** de konfigureres. Trinvise instruktioner om, hvordan hver "
"af disse funktioner opsættes, kan findes i dokumentationen nedenfor:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:364
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:424
msgid ":doc:`WhatsApp <../whatsapp>`"
msgstr ":doc:`WhatsApp <../whatsapp>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/chatter.rst:365
