"<https://www.wipo.int/wipolex/en/legislation/details/14774>`_ and the Law 15 "
"04 of Electronic Signature. The law establishes the legal basis for "
"acknowledging electronic records, contracts, and digital signatures. The key "
"points of the law include:"
msgstr ""
"I Algeriet er elektroniske underskrifter reguleret under `Civil Code "
"<https://www.wipo.int/wipolex/en/legislation/details/14774>`_ og lov 15 04 "
"om elektronisk underskrift. Loven fastlægger det juridiske grundlag for "
"anerkendelse af elektroniske registreringer, kontrakter og digitale "
"underskrifter. Lovens hovedpunkter omfatter:"

