#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/transfer_forward.rst:147
msgid ""
"For more information on forwarding, visit :ref:`voip/axivox/forwardings_tab`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/voip_widget.rst:3
